        "description": "<p>This add-on plugin for bbPress will allow you to place forum-wide notices for alerting your users to important information, such as delayed response times, operating hours, new features, etc.</p>\n<p>If you have suggestions or bugfixes for the plugin, please report them on <a href=\"https://github.com/pippinsplugins/bbPress-Notices\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github</a>.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Activate the plugin</li>\n<li>A new &#8220;Notices&#8221; submenu will be added to the main Forums menu</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed an issue with not being able to edit notices</li>\n<li>Fixed an issue with getting redirected to the Posts list after publishing a notice</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release!</li>\n</ul>\n"
